This class is the request data sent to populate the server's database with generated data for the specified username from request to the database through API endpoint call
FillResult
This class is the response object returned from Fill API endpoint call

This service class implements the function of populating the server's database with generated data for the specified username
LoadRequest
This class is the request data sent to clear and load data from request to the database through API endpoint call
LoadResult
This class is the response object returned from Load API endpoint call
LoadService
This service class implements the function of clearing all data and then loading the user, person, and event data from the request body into the database

This class is the request data sent to log a user in through API endpoint call
LoginResult
This class is the response object returned from Login API endpoint call

This service class implements the function of logining the user in
